<br>
I had at least 2 copies of all the hard cover books, most of the old boxed sets, Dragon Magazine from about issue 6 to 175 or so, plus tons and tons of modules and rules supplements.Also had the original Greyhawk and Forgotten Realms boxed set, and alot of the supplementals for those settings. Everything I had was in great shape too...<br>
<br>
/sigh<br>
<br>
Lost it all in a fire, bleh.<br>
<br>
Might be time to start collecting again.<br>
<br>
